These people and the others officers who have come here

121
00:07:32,704 --> 00:07:36,204
to investigate the accident big brother Keiji got into.

122
00:07:36,904 --> 00:07:39,704
No, I'm not an officer.

123
00:07:39,704 --> 00:07:42,804
You're the one that's no good, Miyuki!

