00:07:49,904 --> 00:07:52,104
How many times do I have to tell you before you understand this?

128
00:07:52,104 --> 00:07:55,604
I'm sorry, Takako.

129
00:07:55,604 --> 00:07:58,604
Never mind that, what did you want, officer?

130
00:07:58,604 --> 00:08:00,504
Just the other day, another police officer

131
00:08:00,504 --> 00:08:02,604
came and left after saying that

132
00:08:02,604 --> 00:08:04,204
it was concluded to be an accident.

133
00:08:04,204 --> 00:08:06,104
Oh, well, I'm not an officer.

134
00:08:06,104 --> 00:08:09,404
However, something that doesn't look like an accident occurred,

135
00:08:09,404 --> 00:08:13,004
