136
00:08:13,004 --> 00:08:15,604
-Right, officer? -You.

137
00:08:15,604 --> 00:08:21,304
Could you be talking of Shinichi who died in Tokyo?

138
00:08:21,304 --> 00:08:24,704
Before he left here, Shinichi said,

139
00:08:24,704 --> 00:08:26,304
a bunch of nonsense about somebody

140
00:08:26,304 --> 00:08:29,104
using a cursed demon dog that is engulfed in flames

141
00:08:29,104 --> 00:08:30,604
to annihilate the bloodline of Inubushi from its roots.

142
00:08:30,604 --> 00:08:32,704
Is that what you're referring to?

143
00:08:32,704 --> 00:08:36,504
But there's no such thing as a curse, so no need for worry.

144
00:08:36,504 --> 00:08:40,904
Besides, if mother hears of this, it will make her sad.

145
00:08:41,704 --> 00:08:44,104
Is Satomi here?

146
