Yes. It seems to date back to the Meiji Era, though.

192
00:10:53,604 --> 00:10:56,504
All of the townspeople were helping to look for the only daughter

193
00:10:56,504 --> 00:10:58,704
of the Inubushi family, who suddenly disappeared,

