00:11:43,504 --> 00:11:44,604
Yes.

211
00:11:44,604 --> 00:11:48,304
Under the cliff that your car almost fell from this afternoon.

212
00:11:48,304 --> 00:11:51,004
Would you like me to take you there right now?

